<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.4.7">
<l>pukarā ruruvā kimuṉin tavaṉaip pukaḻvī ṭamuṉin tuyiruṇ ṭacuraṉ</l>
<l>nakarā yiṉapāḻ paṭanā mameṟin tatuvaṉ ṟiyumveṉ ṟikoḷvā ḷavuṇaṉ</l>
<l>pakarā tavaṉā yiranā mamaṭip paṇiyā tavaṉaip paṇiyā lamaril</l>
<l>nikarā yavaṉneñ ciṭantā ṉavaṉuk kiṭammā malaiyā vatunīr malaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place for the one who, by request, dug into the chest of him</l>
<l rend="indent">who was his equal in battle, him who would not say</l>
<l rend="indent">[the lord’s] thousand names,</l>
<l>The one who did not bow at his feet, the demon with a victorious sword,</l>
<l>As well as having raged to end the glory of the one who raged</l>
<l rend="indent">becoming a splendor-filled form, [his] destroying [that one’s] name,</l>
<l>Consuming his life, as [he] made a wasteland</l>
<l rend="indent">where the demon’s city had been, is the great mountain, namely Nīrmalai.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
